OOC: Catching up on all of my guys in one post
IC:
                         Waspinator

Waspinator had fallen asleep when he heard Megatron over the com 
link, startled he flew straight up and crashed into the 
roof "Waspinator not do anything!, no do nothing!" Wasponator yelled 
over the com link while he flew around the room chaoticly

                         Quickstrike

"How long before we can slag something?!" Quickstrike demanded of 
UltraByte.


                          Inferno

Inferno was still in stasis lock, headless, the the brige, fortunitly 
his ant like form allowed him to sustain like this for an extension 
of time.

                          Kenzo

Kenzo had just finished compiling the data from repairing Nightlight 
then leaned back in his chair to rest for a bit.
